title: 1907–08 Hibernian F.C. season
text: During the 1907–08 season <a href="Hibernian%20F.C.">Hibernian</a>, a <a href="association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Edinburgh">Edinburgh</a>, finished sixth out of 18 clubs in the <a href="Scottish%20First%20Division">Scottish First Division</a>.
